    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car at a lower price point. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, while the interior shows clear signs of wear, including some staining on the upholstery. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it does have a slow oil leak and will likely need new brake pads and tires in the near future. It\u2019s a reliable daily driver for now, but expect to put in some maintenance work to keep it in good shape.",
