      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a superlative example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, a testament to its fastidious maintenance history and sheltered storage. Every detail, from the pristine interior upholstery to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a standard of care that satisfies the most discerning collector. We invite you to experience this peerless acquisition, which delivers the refinement and performance of a new vehicle.",
